data.description: Step into paradise with this beautifully remodeled 55+ retirement home in the sought-after Paradise Gardens. A haven of tranquility, this home features neutral tile floors, upgraded bathrooms, & the added safety of hurricane impact windows & doors. The NEWER Rheem AC & WATER HEATER ensure modern comfort, while the upgraded kitchen, adorned with white shaker cabinets, imparts a clean and fresh aesthetic.  The spacious layout includes a separate family room overlooking a serene lake, enhancing the peaceful ambiance. The roof replacement, complete with a ridge vent, contributes to the home's cool atmosphere, while the attic reinsulation further ensures energy efficiency. Embrace the essence of retirement living in this thoughtfully updated home, where comfort meets elegance. MOVE IN READY & FULLY REMODELED 2/2 WATERFRONT RETIREMENT HOME WITH ONE CAR GARAGE; HURRICANE IMPACT WINDOWS; NEWER ROOF, AC & WATER HEATER & UPGRADED KITCHEN & BATHROOMS AND SPACIOUS LAYOUT. Nothing in this home is builders grade.
